195f48379128922d5631423586d5","tid":300241,"uid":55552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-29T02:17:28.000Z","msg":"數學足以"},{"pid":"fd07d738a149bdf8e69156268cbc259c9b62da76","tid":300241,"uid":8883,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-29T02:34:49.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>~(A&cap;B)∷~A&cup;~B<br />\n<br />\nA&rarr;B∷~A&cup;B</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n你個名<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nDe Moivre's law同material implication真係少啲想像力都諗唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我教material implication既時候都係大部分學生聽唔明<br />\n可能我講得1999<br />\n但我已經將d steps講哂出黎 仲試過連埋例子講<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b88c01e1082c6acd5de260955ff403ed4180a48f","tid":300241,"uid":37735,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-29T02:37:12.000Z","msg":"學科化有好有壞<br />\n好易徒有表面<br />\n<br />\n法國哲學200年歷史<br />\n<br />\n人人話好 <br />\n但歷史 社會 無一樣野體現到200年哲學精神 <br />\n<br />\n流於作答 背答案<br />\n先唔講好像第3共和  簡直係人類民主其中一個極差示範<br />\n<br />\n法國大選<br />\n咪又係左一句民粹 右一句煽動仇恨"},{"pid":"1586302924df1f0999edd00ffea0dc367adbe868","tid":300241,"uid":93732,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-29T02:37:28.000Z","msg":"數學同通識已經訓練緊邏輯同思考"},{"pid":"c898b5b8f74ef6a0841abbeeb4530cd0220ee8cd","tid":300241,"uid":92017,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-29T02:39:30.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>~(A&cap;B)∷~A&cup;~B<br />\n<br />\nA&rarr;B∷~A&cup;B</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n你個名<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nDe Moivre's law同material implication真係少啲想像力都諗唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我教material implication既時候都係大部分學生聽唔明<br />\n可能我講得1999<br />\n但我已經將d steps講哂出黎 仲試過連埋例子講<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n巴打 睇A Concise Introduction to Logic 是否夠入門？"},{"pid":"a6b68db7e07b92eea3c92fee22afc7460e336308","tid":300241,"uid":92301,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-29T02:39:38.000Z","msg":"月經"},{"pid":"66803f6b5c1ea26ef49acf9718ca32753200295d","tid":300241,"uid":34301,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-29T04:26:54.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>~(A&cap;B)∷~A&cup;~B<br />\n<br />\nA&rarr;B∷~A&cup;B</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n你個名<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">De Morgan's law</span>同material implication真係少啲想像力都諗唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我教material implication既時候都係大部分學生聽唔明<br />\n可能我講得1999<br />\n但我已經將d steps講哂出黎 仲試過連埋例子講<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n係De Morgan's law唔係De Moivre's law 撈鳩亂咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n一開始畀個truth table佢哋睇先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ac5bacc0cda6fe4662f3722777905e485001d155","tid":300241,"uid":34301,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-29T04:36:25.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>數學同通識已經訓練緊邏輯同思考</blockquote><br />\n通識都重可以講下<br />\n老老竇竇我覺得通識無明確訓練學生邊種思考模式<br />\n但我估個框架其實都係phenomenon -&gt; issue/problem -&gt; cause, impacts, solutions -&gt; other related issues<br />\n呢種思考模式好處就係夠晒實用，例如喺構思政策嗰陣都幾有用<br />\n但係好處同時都係壞處，就係呢種模式太貼地，正常人好難用呢套框架思考哲學問題<br />\n與其話通識訓練緊學生嘅思考能力，倒不如話佢其實係灌輸一啲基本概念畀學生再等佢哋自由發揮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5878bc0f16c56ee0b9ecbf9df188bac89938feb5","tid":300241,"uid":34301,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-29T04:39:36.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>~(A&cap;B)∷~A&cup;~B<br />\n<br />\nA&rarr;B∷~A&cup;B</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n你個名<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nDe Moivre's law同material implication真係少啲想像力都諗唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我教material implication既時候都係大部分學生聽唔明<br />\n可能我講得1999<br />\n但我已經將d steps講哂出黎 仲試過連埋例子講<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n巴打 睇A Concise Introduction to Logic 是否夠入門？</blockquote><br />\n夠入門<br />\n不過我覺得用呢本嘢自學會好辛苦<br />\n因為佢exercise嘅solution太少"},{"pid":"90a292a18f723c2e00bc75857b24a3f2e3e25fc4","tid":300241,"uid":92017,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-29T04:53:05.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>~(A&cap;B)∷~A&cup;~B<br />\n<br />\nA&rarr;B∷~A&cup;B</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n你個名<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nDe Moivre's law同material implication真係少啲想像力都諗唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我教material implication既時候都係大部分學生聽唔明<br />\n可能我講得1999<br />\n但我已經將d steps講哂出黎 仲試過連埋例子講<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n巴打 睇A Concise Introduction to Logic 是否夠入門？</blockquote><br />\n夠入門<br />\n不過我覺得用呢本嘢自學會好辛苦<br />\n因為佢exercise嘅solution太少</blockquote><br />\n最classic個本introduction to logic會好d?"},{"pid":"8850f0c4a96a0bbd4a51c3a82c95173c2bda9fb2","tid":300241,"uid":34301,"like"